Installation
------------

1. Login as root.

2. Enter the following commands to unpack the driver source code.

# tar -jxvf acsccid-x.y.z.tar.bz2
# cd acsccid-x.y.z

3. To build the driver in Linux, please install development tools and 
   the following dependencies.

# libtool
# autoconf

  Enter the following commands to build and install the driver.

# autoreconf -i
# ./configure
# make
# make install

4. To build the driver in Mac OS X, please install development tools from
   Apple and install libusb. Enter the following commands to install the
   driver.

# ./MacOSX/configure
# make
# make install
